
                                            Amina J Mohammed delivers the 15th Nelson Mandela Annual Lecture on 25 November 2017.
                                         CAPE TOWN - People from across Africa have come to attend the 15th Nelson Mandela Annual Lecture at the Cape Town International Convention Centre on Saturday. This year's speaker is UN Deputy Secretary-General Amina Mohammed, under the theme ‘Gender - Reducing Inequality Through Inclusion.’ 